<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="義解" xml:id="gsz0731a05shiSengYuan"><lb
ed="T" n="0731a05"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0731a05"/><head><date from-iso="+0689-12-21" key="j19730671978610" to-iso="+0705-02-24">周</date><placeName key="PL000000009973">虎丘山寺</placeName><persName key="A009245">僧瑗</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0731a06"/><persName key="A009245">釋僧瑗</persName>，字<persName key="A009245">辯空</persName>，姓<name>郁</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000022911"><placeName>高平</placeName><placeName>昌邑</placeName></placeName>人也。<placeName key="PL000000056129">姬水</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0731a07"/>疏源，<placeName key="PL000000020418">狼亭</placeName><ptr target="#n96"/>襲慶──<persName key="A021624">魯<roleName>相</roleName></persName>繼<persName key="A002160">昌<roleName>侯</roleName></persName>之業，歷載彌<lb
ed="T" n="0731a08"/>光<ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n648"/>；少<anchor xml:id="beg0731sgsz1"/>傅<anchor xml:id="end0731sgsz1"/>纂尚書之風，清塵不昧。<persName key="A009245">瑗</persName>夙殖<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g90"/>奇<lb
ed="T" n="0731a09"/>頴，早擅嘉祥<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g649"/>。母<persName key="A021628">趙<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>娠孕之日，側侍聖賢<lb
ed="T" n="0731a10"/>浮空遊樂。及<date key="j19562761956641" from-iso="+0644-01-01" to-iso="+0644-12-31">年六歲</date>，隨<ref type="person" target="#A021628">母</ref>入舍利塔，見聖<lb
ed="T" n="0731a11"/>僧像<ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n650"/>，欣然跳躍，狀若舊交，因啟<ref type="person" target="#A021628">母</ref>出家。<ref type="person" target="#A021628">母</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0731a12"/>以<ref type="person" target="#A009245">其</ref>尚幼，抑而未許。至<date key="j19588331959197" from-iso="+0651-01-01" to-iso="+0651-12-31">年十三</date>，方遂<ref type="person" target="#A009245">其</ref>志，<lb
ed="T" n="0731a13"/>依<placeName key="PL000000009973">虎丘寺</placeName><persName key="A009246">慧嚴<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>為弟子。謙揖之操，出<lb
ed="T" n="0731a14"/>自生知；辯慧之能，業稱上首。以<date from-iso="+0662-01-28" key="j19628781963261" to-iso="+0663-02-15"><name>龍朔</name>二年</date><lb
ed="T" n="0731a15"/>奉勅剃翦，冥符所應，還隷<ref type="place" target="#PL000000010007">此山</ref>。暨<persName key="A009246">嚴<roleName>公</roleName></persName>長<lb
ed="T" n="0731a16"/>往，乃依<persName key="A009247">慧詡<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>受具足戒，聽<placeName key="PL000000009888">常樂寺</placeName><persName key="A007009">聰<lb
ed="T" n="0731a17"/><roleName>法師</roleName></persName>三《論》<ptr target="#n1551"/>，甚深無相，疑滯豁除，方便解脫，怡<lb
ed="T" n="0731a18"/>然獨悟。因智從心證，遂詣<placeName key="PL000000008820">江寧</placeName><persName key="A003867">融<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>求<lb
ed="T" n="0731a19"/>學心法。攝念坐禪，眾魔斯伏；勤行精進，猛獸<lb
ed="T" n="0731a20"/>恒馴。是以名稱普聞，聲光八絕<ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n651"/>，旗亭<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g652"/>趨利，削<lb
ed="T" n="0731a21"/>跡無踐。冬夏不易，常披一納。或滴水以充<lb
ed="T" n="0731a22"/>於夕渴，或數粒將濟於朝飢。或風雪凜凜，<anchor xml:id="beg0731sgsz2"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0731sgsz2"/><lb
ed="T" n="0731a23"/>誦無替<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g522"/>於六時；或炎暑爞爞<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g653"/>，經行<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1047"/>不虧於<lb
ed="T" n="0731a24"/>少選<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g654"/>。稱揚歎<anchor xml:id="beg0731sgsz4"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>羡</sic><corr>羨</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0731sgsz4"/><ptr target="#n1087"/>，容色湛如；毀辱訶罵，歡喜而<lb
ed="T" n="0731a25"/>受。每蔭以長松，屬思鴻遠。清泉獨坐，映定<lb
ed="T" n="0731a26"/>水以彫文；虛室高栖，藹禪枝而蕩慮。撰《武<lb
ed="T" n="0731a27"/>丘名僧苑》一卷、注《郁子》兩卷、《文集》三卷，蓋道<lb
ed="T" n="0731a28"/>俗之儀表，人物之師範焉。<date key="j19731151973115" when-iso="+0690-02-07"><name>永昌</name>元年十二月<lb
ed="T" n="0731a29"/>二十日</date>見身有疾，謂弟子曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A009245">吾</ref>聞屍所到<pb ed="T" n="0731b" xml:id="T50.2061.0731b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0731b01"/>處，便為穢惡，出就別方，乃稱離罪爾。」門弟<lb
ed="T" n="0731b02"/>子等迎止於<placeName>通波亭</placeName>北<placeName key="PL000000009849">靜志莊</placeName>，忽聞異香從<lb
ed="T" n="0731b03"/>空而下。<persName key="A009245">瑗</persName>遺訓勤切，正觀叮嚀，滅後可依<lb
ed="T" n="0731b04"/>外國法。言訖合掌而終，春秋五十有一。緇素<lb
ed="T" n="0731b05"/>奔慟，咸悲眼滅。弟子僧<persName key="A009248">義<anchor xml:id="beg0731sgsz6"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>立</sic><corr>玄</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0731sgsz6"/><ptr target="#n655"/></persName>及<placeName key="PL000000011957">雉山縣</placeName>尉檀<lb
ed="T" n="0731b06"/>信等同遵<ref type="person" target="#A009245">師</ref>旨，如法闍維，收其舍利，於寺<lb
ed="T" n="0731b07"/>建塔，勒銘于所。</p>
